review_blob: Cherry taste all over. Sprizzy refreshing, sweet and yet I am able to drink several of them in a row.

Discovered at Stockholm Beer & Whiskey festival. The perfect beer to drink between richer types of beer. Very refreshing. Great beer to introduce to girls/people who dont think they lile beer very much.
Unbelievable beer experience! Nothing to just drink away. Take your time, relax, be in no hurry while you experience the most rich berry beer explosion in your mouth!
beer_name: Struise Black Damnation I - Black Berry Albert

review_blob: Great summer beer with the fruity taste of banana. Am usually no Weizen-fan but this one really is one of my favorites. Very refreshing, yet no fruit beer.
Great beer. Enjoyed the oak taste and richness of this beer, still not getting tired of the taste throughout one bottle/glas.
beer_name: Innis & Gunn Oak Aged Blonde Beer
